summary:
After the realization set in that I will not be making it as a pro football player (I was never close), my next dream was to become an online marketing expert. Currently I am working as a communications advisor at the Wageningen University & Research, where I make sure the online journey of our visitors is tailored as closely as possible to the needs of the visitor.
